latest stuff for the server
Implemented Server Side Auth. Added Memcache, and a proxy server to the gruntfile. Use grunt proxy server and start the flask server now.
removed htaccess nonsense from yeoman
clean up
removed dead bugzilla module
started bugzilla proxy in flask. laid out endpoint for new /board methods.
removed some old code
fixes crash when viewing custom boards that don't exist
bumped up fontsize on popovers and comment modal now autofocuses when appearing.
added ability to post comments on bugs with a comment modal
changed jquery-ui dependency to a minimal version of jquery ui containing only the core and sortable stuff
fixed popovers by removing the include_fields from the interceptor and just including it in the /bug api calls
fixed firefox click card bug when dropping cards in the same column
added styling to card being dragged.
updated bower deps. removed placeholder dom element for empty list sorting and replaced it with some padding
can now drag and drop between columns. fixed chrome compositing issue caused by animating opacity on hover of cards and then dragging that card around. Just removed the animations, works kthnx
angular-ui-sortable directive version of card sorting, doesn't have connected lists at the moment though
moved cards into li tags
added last comment action to cards. Also have to hover over cards to display actions now. cuts down on a lot of the clutter.
removed some old lines
removed old draggable directive
started drag/drop on cards and the settings sidebar on the board pages
added tooltips for descriptions
removed some dom structure out of cards

refactored lots of html out of boards and into individual column components. need to figure how this could impact dragging and dropping of cards though because it removes a lot of power from the boards controller and gives it to the columns controller and dragging and dropping between columns should arguably be the responsibility of the boards controller
removed some dead stuff in the board
adding additional actions to cards
can now create new boards, and custom boards will query for all components attached to them. Need to clean that code up a bit though.
starting to create custom boards
removed some old code
some build fixes. commented out the saving to localstorage of uname/pword. Have to relogin on page visits now.
build now working, css important (couldn't figure out why there's bootstrap being included where its not supposed to be in the build.
jshint warning fixes. add images to copy task in gruntfile
changed filters for each status into individual get requests. Boards now done by component/product/custom. Custom boards still need work.
changed /board route to support products and compnents as well as custom boards
login stuff
added bugzilla auth interceptor and auth service boilerplate
added to bugzilla service, auth soon to come
fixed bug where shrinking columns when scrolled to right would get you stuck. Now reset position to 0 when no need for scroll
fixed scrollbar to disappear when shrinking columns
fixed resizing drop zone width on column resizing
changed mainctrl into boardctrl, and fixed bug that was executing the angular app twice. it was class=ng-view
